            <lg xml:id="TK232">
<l>uraippā ruraippavai yellā mirappārkkoṉ</l>
<l>ṟīvārmē ṉiṟkum pukaḻ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whatsoever is spoken in the world will abide as praise upon that man who gives alms to the poor.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
